# Draft:Queen Azzyah

----
Queen Azzyah is a 19 Year Old rapper and singer-songwriter, whose real name is Judiah Taylor. She is known for hip hop music her popular songs listed on her discography include "Step 1 Step 2" and "Get Down". Her music is available on various streaming platforms, including Spotify, Apple Music, Pandora, and AllMusic. She Was Born June, 2 2006 and is a Gemini.
